<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.4">
<l>cakkarak kaiyaṉ taṭaṅkaṇṇāl malara viḻit</l>
<l>tokkalai mēlirun tuṉṉaiyē cuṭṭik kāṭṭuṅkāṇ</l>
<l>takka taṟitiyēl canti rācalam ceyyātē</l>
<l>makkaṭ peṟāta malaṭa ṉallaiyēl vākaṇṭāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He whose hands [hold] the discus opened [his] big eyes wide,</l>
<l>sitting on my hip, [he] points out and reveals you, see!</l>
<l>If you know what is proper, Moon, do not deceive [him],</l>
<l>if you are not a sterile man who has not begotten children, come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
